      <div class="grid group nopadding comment-wrap" id="comment-82907">

        <div class="comment-avatar grid-1-5">
          <img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/96ee269a18aae62266477d1390f5e9db?s=160&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fcss-tricks.com%2Fimages%2Fget-gravatar.png%3Fs%3D160&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-160 photo' height='160' width='160' />        </div>

        <div class="comment-body group grid-4-5">

          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-author"><a href='http://ajcates.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>A.J. Cates</a></div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="http://css-tricks.com/box-sizing/#comment-82907"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</span></a> <time pubdate datetime="2010-09-10T11:59:01+00:00">September 10, 2010</time></div>
            
          </div>
          
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>You can also use `display: table` to throw items into border-box sizing mode.</p>

